snippet.title: CryptoGrounds
snippet.description:
Hello!
I am an 18 year old Game Developer and Programming Enthusiast!
I make daily programming and gaming related videos.

My channel is special because I post content for anyone who loves games and wants to learn how to code, use unity, or want to become a game developer! I do my best to help everyone when it comes to my tutorials and I be sure to explain everything perfectly! My goal is to have you learn something new after watching one or more of my videos! :D

Like if you enjoy my videos, share these videos and playlists to your friends who would enjoy them as well and let them know to leave a like! Every like motivates me to create the best and the most informative and helpful content just for you guys :)

Subscribe if you are new and turn on notifications to get notified for my daily videos!

~~ SUPPORT ME~~
Discord: https://discord.gg/S9mtMTw
PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/cryptogrounds
MERCH: https://teespring.com/stores/cryptogrounds-merch
